<p>Live Customization offers you two handy tools that are intended to help you translate and modify LiveCart's graphical interface. "Live Customization" lets you locate and edit source code templates. That is you can change and save code templates directly in the graphical user interface (GUI). When the "Live translation mode" is turned on you can translate menus and captions directly in the GUI.</p> 	

